Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.68,0:29:12.00,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,Plano quatro:
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.58,0:29:15.92,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,Chamá-lo pelo Den Den Mushi e \Ndizer para se apressarem e fugirem.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.86,0:29:27.62,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,Ah, eu não tenho um.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.87,0:29:32.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Não se aproxime!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.00,0:29:39.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Mesmo que eu pudesse avisá-lo, \Neles não teriam tempo para fugir!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.02,0:29:50.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Vamos lá!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.44,0:29:51.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Pica-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.86,0:29:55.77,Main,,0,0,0,,Ele quer acabar com o Rei Riku!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.65,0:30:00.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Não é da nossa conta, \Nmas eu não gosto disso!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.98,0:30:02.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Pare!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.72,0:30:04.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Monstro de pedra!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.65,0:30:07.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Sogeking-senpai está naquele platô!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.27,0:30:09.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Pedra!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.52,0:30:10.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Volte!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.83,0:30:13.40,Main,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,988)}Eu vou lutar com você!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.78,0:30:21.44,Main,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,700)}Não!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.26,0:30:30.51,Main,,0,0,0,,Já sei!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.51,0:30:36.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Que bom que guardei meu King Punch como o Caçador de Piratas me disse!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.28,0:30:43.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Agora eu vou te salvar!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.32,0:30:44.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Rei Riku, meu amigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.96,0:30:46.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Espere um segundo, rei de sei lá onde!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.90,0:30:48.57,Main,,0,0,0,,De sei lá onde?!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.57,0:30:51.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Eu sou Elizabello, o rei de Prodence,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.20,0:30:53.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Caçador de Piratas!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.36,0:30:56.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Já disse que não adianta destruí-lo.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.08,0:30:59.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Se não o derrotarmos, \Nele voltará de novo e de novo!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.37,0:31:01.08,Main,,0,0,0,,E então o que fazemos?!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.13,0:31:09.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Socorro!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.28,0:31:14.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Caçador de Piratas!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.25,0:31:41.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Ei!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.47,0:31:42.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Me dê dois minutos.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.21,0:31:47.46,Main,,0,0,0,,O Rei Riku está aí?!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.12,0:31:54.47,OPLetreros2,,0,0,0,,{\fscx270\fscy270\pos(618,138)}PLANO 5
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.09,0:31:54.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Plano cinco.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.47,0:31:54.85,OPLetreros2,,0,0,0,,{\fscx270\fscy270\pos(634,96)}VOAR
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.47,0:31:57.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Voar pelos céus e cortá-lo em pedaços!
