Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.42,0:32:06.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Vamos fazer isso!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.48,0:32:21.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Se não fizermos algo...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.91,0:32:23.00,Main,,0,0,0,,O avô e os outros vão...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.00,0:32:26.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Sogeking-senpai! Corra!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.01,0:32:38.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Caçador de Piratas!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.16,0:32:41.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Até quando tenho que esperar?!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.68,0:32:43.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Ei, diretor!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.10,0:32:44.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Hã?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.20,0:32:46.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Se você quer dizer "Comodoro", sou eu.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.31,0:32:47.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Tanto faz!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.81,0:32:50.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Você lançou uma pessoa \Ncomo se fosse uma bala, não foi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.18,0:32:56.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Prepare-se, Rei Riku!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.16,0:33:00.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Atirem, atirem!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.54,0:33:16.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Eu sou seu alvo, certo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.22,0:33:19.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Não cause mais estragos!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.48,0:33:24.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Escutem todos!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.74,0:33:26.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Fujam rápido!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.54,0:33:28.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Desçam deste platô!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.95,0:33:39.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Rei Riku, você também\N precisa fugir rápido!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.83,0:33:42.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Rápido, pai!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.81,0:33:44.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Viola, Tank!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.58,0:33:46.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Levem todos para baixo, rápido!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.72,0:33:48.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Eu sou o alvo dele!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.60,0:33:49.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Vão!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.92,0:33:52.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Por isso você deve fugir, Rei Riku!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.26,0:33:54.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Rápido!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.21,0:33:55.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Não!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.16,0:33:59.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Se todos puderem escapar \Nenquanto ele se concentra em mim,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.36,0:34:01.60,Main,,0,0,0,,ficarei satisfeito!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.74,0:34:04.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Entendi!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.54,0:34:07.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Então, que seja como você deseja!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.24,0:34:19.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Que diabos?!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.65,0:34:21.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Caçador de Piratas, Orlumbus!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.60,0:34:23.04,Main,,0,0,0,,O que vocês estão planejando?!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.04,0:34:25.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Você tem certeza disso?!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.54,0:34:29.19,Main,,0,0,0,,Essa técnica não foi feita para \Nlançar alguém sem machucar!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.19,0:34:30.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Faça logo!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.54,0:34:31.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Não há tempo!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.25,0:34:33.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Esse idiota...!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.15,0:34:35.51,Main,,0,0,0,,Ele só ataca quem \Nnão quer lutar!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.51,0:34:37.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Lá vamos nós!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.15,0:34:37.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.35,0:34:45.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Rei Riku, você não é um rei!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.30,0:34:47.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Nem você tem o necessário \Npara ser um rei!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.19,0:34:52.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Teitoku...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.16,0:35:09.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Sua Majestade, se você não \Nvai fugir, nós também não!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.29,0:35:13.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Rei Riku, você esclareceu o \Nmal-entendido de uma década atrás...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.46,0:35:16.84,Main,,0,0,0,,...e recuperou sua popularidade?!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.84,0:35:20.51,Main,,0,0,0,,Já esqueceu que, por ser pacifista...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.51,0:35:25.08,Main,,0,0,0,,...não conseguiu proteger seu país?!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.08,0:35:27.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Um país significa poder militar!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.25,0:35:29.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Alguém que não pode \Ndestruir o inimigo...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.94,0:35:32.81,Main,,0,0,0,,...não está qualificado para ser rei!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.61,0:35:39.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Vou esmagar você junto \Ncom seus ideais tolos!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.49,0:35:41.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Rei Riku!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.28,0:35:48.45,Main,,0,0,0,,A-A cidade está caindo!!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.21,0:35:57.05,Main,,0,0,0,,...Killer...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.05,0:35:58.34,Main,,0,0,0,,...Bowling!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.03,0:36:20.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Você está certo!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.75,0:36:23.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Não consegui proteger o país, \Nsou um incompetente!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.32,0:36:25.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Não vou retomar o trono!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.86,0:36:26.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Rei Riku!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.87,0:36:28.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Mas...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.29,0:36:31.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Me esforcei demais para ser um homem!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.52,0:36:39.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Nove montanhas e oito mares...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.59,0:36:41.16,Main,,0,0,0,,...constituem um mundo!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.70,0:36:44.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Mil deles formam um chiliocosmos!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.48,0:36:47.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Ao unir três,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.86,0:36:50.36,Main,,0,0,0,,não há nada que eu não possa cortar!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.28,0:36:55.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Santouryuu Ougi!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.94,0:36:59.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Por ser um homem?!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.15,0:37:03.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Se não posso viver \Nsem cometer um assassinato,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.16,0:37:06.70,Main,,0,0,0,,então, escolho a morte!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.22,0:37:10.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Uma nação repleta de \Nmassacres não tem futuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.41,0:37:14.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Sua Majestade, você é nosso único rei!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.20,0:37:21.51,Main,,0,0,0,,Por isso, os bons não fazem história!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.51,0:37:26.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Porque morrem como você!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.82,0:37:32.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Ichidai Sanzen...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.00,0:37:36.02,Main,,0,0,0,,...Daisen Sekai!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.96,0:38:19.53,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,Certo, ele fugiu para a parte superior do corpo!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.53,0:38:20.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Roronoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.94,0:38:47.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.18,0:38:57.02,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,Pedras mortas...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.02,0:38:59.10,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,Pedras que se movem...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.10,0:39:03.48,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,Não importa em quantos pedaços se dividam, o verdadeiro definitivamente...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.48,0:39:05.38,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,...estará em um deles!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.53,0:39:09.53,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,Não vai se dividir!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.88,0:39:29.80,Main,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.88,0:39:29.80,Secondary,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.69,0:39:47.61,Main,,0,0,0,,No ar, não há terra para onde ir!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.24,0:39:52.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Apareça, Pica!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.10,0:40:06.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Até quando você vai \Ncontinuar se escondendo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.28,0:40:10.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Você pretende ganhar...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.54,0:40:13.22,Main,,0,0,0,,...me encurralando?!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.88,0:40:25.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Você acha que pode me \Nvencer cortando pedras?!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.48,0:40:28.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Você não poderá me cortar \Nquando eu estiver coberto de Haki!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.91,0:40:35.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Haki, hein?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.16,0:40:38.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Se eu te nocautear, você perde!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.87,0:40:43.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Só se o seu Haki for \Nmais forte que o meu!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.29,0:40:48.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Não tenho tempo para \Nlidar com alguém do seu nível!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.00,0:40:49.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Não encha!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.16,0:40:54.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Nove montanhas e oito mares!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.09,0:40:55.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Não há nada que eu não possa cortar!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.97,0:40:58.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Morra!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.22,0:41:00.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Roronoa Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.48,0:41:02.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Sanzen Sekai!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.11,0:41:10.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Não incomode as pessoas honestas!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.28,0:41:13.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Zoro-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.77,0:41:16.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Doro! {Zoro!}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.77,0:41:16.16,Secondary,,0,0,0,,(Zoro).
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.91,0:41:25.25,Main,,0,0,0,,O Caçador de Piratas \Nsalvou meu amigo, o Rei Riku...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.95,0:41:35.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Mas mesmo assim ele está \Ncaindo sobre nós!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.09,0:41:39.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Vamos morrer!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.97,0:41:43.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Socorro, Boro!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.97,0:41:43.06,Secondary,,0,0,0,,(Socorro, Zoro).
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.97,0:41:50.07,Main,,0,0,0,,É a sua vez!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.65,0:41:56.61,Main,,0,0,0,,King...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.61,0:41:59.99,Main,,0,0,0,,...Punch!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.91,0:42:30.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Aquele moleque usou meu King Punch...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.39,0:42:32.08,Main,,0,0,0,,...para limpar os escombros!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.08,0:42:33.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Que insolente!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.36,0:42:34.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Ele vai se arrepender por isso!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.67,0:42:37.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Bom trabalho!
